tests.title: /Email_correto
/Senha_Correta
tests.code:
cy //insert correct pass
.get('#inputPassword').type('123456789') //click submit
.get('.btn').click() //verify span error
.get('#passwordHelp').should('be.visible');

tests.title: /Email_vazio
tests.code:
cy //insert empty email
.get('#staticEmail').type('aa') //clear values from email
.clear() //click submit
.get('.btn').click() //expect message error
.get(':nth-child(1) > #passwordHelp').should('be.visible') //with this value
.contains('O email está vazio');
